    "result": {"data":{"strapiPost":{"strapiId":3949,"title":"No Kill Animal Center Is Underway","topic":"Animals","slug":"no-kill-animal-center-is-underway","coverImage":{"publicURL":"/static/2dac7ca452387d9c33b8f62017ce772c/b4201ee84098b6d8356c9a8c8fd8a7b9.jpg"},"photoCredit":"Best Friends","date":"2021-12-07","content":"<p>A new “<a href=\"https://bestfriends.org/no-kill-2025/what-does-no-kill-mean\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">no-kill</a>” center for pets is underway in Bentonville, and it hit a <a href=\"https://www.nwahomepage.com/news/raise-the-woof-bentonville-pet-resource-centers-construction-sees-final-beam-placed/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">construction milestone</a> this past weekend — the final steal beam was put on top of the building, completing its frame.</p><ul><li><strong>Like no other: </strong>It will be called <a href=\"https://bestfriends.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Best Friends</a> Pet Rescue Center, and it will be a space <a href=\"https://bestfriends.org/stories/julie-castle-blog/best-friends-partners-walton-family-foundation-launch-new-era-animal\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">unlike</a> any other. Animals will be up for adoption, pet services will be available for low income families, and other programs and educational resources will be provided for everyone.</li><li><strong>Connected: </strong>The center will be located in Bentonville’s 8th St Gateway Park and is set to be <a href=\"https://bestfriends.org/locations/best-friends-northwest-arkansas/campaign/timeline-and-design\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">complete</a> in summer 2022. Best Friends is accepting general <a href=\"https://support.bestfriends.org/site/Donation2?df_id=1949&amp;mfc_pref=T&amp;1949.donation=form1&amp;_ga=2.160101566.2095626753.1638740198-2122866399.1638740198\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">donations</a> for sustaining <a href=\"https://bestfriends.org/no-kill-2025/our-priorities-2025\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">no-kill communities</a> as well as for the <a href=\"https://support.bestfriends.org/site/Donation2?3625.donation=form1&amp;df_id=3625&amp;mfc_pref=T\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">current project</a>.</li></ul><p>Learn more <a href=\"https://bestfriends.org/locations/save-homeless-pets-northwest-arkansas/campaign\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a>.&nbsp;</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"no-kill-animal-center-is-underway"}},
